import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; import axios from 'axios'; import ServiceManagement from '../components/ServiceManagement'; import BookingManagement from '../components/BookingManagement'; const Dashboard = () => { const { user } = useSelector(state => state.auth); const [providerData, setProviderData] = useState(null); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); const [error, setError] = useState(null); const [showCreateModal, setShowCreateModal] = useState(false); const [createFormData, setCreateFormData] = useState({ // Provider Information name: '', description: '', category: 'education', subcategory: '', address: '', contact_phone: '', website: '', years_experience: '', qualifications: '', languages: '', target_age_groups: '', teaching_methodology: '', specializations: '', offers_trial: false, trial_description: '', // Service Information service_name: '', service_description: '', service_type: 'individual', duration_hours: 1, duration_minutes: 0, max_participants: 1, session_format: 'in_person', // in_person, online, hybrid materials_included: '', prerequisites: '', // Pricing Information pricing_type: 'per_session', price: '', currency: 'USD', pricing_description: '', min_sessions: 1, max_sessions: null, group_discount_available: false, group_discount_description: '' }); const [createLoading, setCreateLoading] = useState(false); useEffect(() => { if (user?.user_type === 'provider') { fetchProviderData(); } else { setLoading(false); } }, [user]); const fetchProviderData = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get('/api/providers/my/'); setProviderData(response.data); } catch (error) { if (error.response?.status === 404) { // Provider profile not found - this is expected for new providers setProviderData(null); } else { setError('Failed to load provider data'); } } finally { setLoading(false); } }; const handleCreateSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); setCreateLoading(true); setError(null); try { // Step 1: Create provider profile const providerResponse = await axios.post('/api/providers/my/', { name: createFormData.name, description: createFormData.description, category: createFormData.category, subcategory: createFormData.subcategory, address: createFormData.address }); // Step 2: Create service const serviceResponse = await axios.post('/api/providers/services/', { name: createFormData.service_name, description: createFormData.service_description, service_type: createFormData.service_type, duration_hours: parseInt(createFormData.duration_hours), duration_minutes: parseInt(createFormData.duration_minutes), max_participants: parseInt(createFormData.max_participants) }); // Step 3: Create pricing for the service await axios.post(`/api/providers/services/${serviceResponse.data.id}/pricing/`, { pricing_type: createFormData.pricing_type, price: parseFloat(createFormData.price), currency: createFormData.currency, description: createFormData.pricing_description, min_sessions: parseInt(createFormData.min_sessions), max_sessions: createFormData.max_sessions ? parseInt(createFormData.max_sessions) : null }); // Refresh provider data await fetchProviderData(); setShowCreateModal(false); setCreateFormData({ name: '', description: '', category: 'education', subcategory: '', address: '', service_name: '', service_description: '', service_type: 'individual', duration_hours: 1, duration_minutes: 0, max_participants: 1, pricing_type: 'per_session', price: '', currency: 'USD', pricing_description: '', min_sessions: 1, max_sessions: null }); } catch (error) { setError(error.response?.data?.detail || 'Failed to create provider profile and services'); } finally { setCreateLoading(false); } }; const handleCreateChange = (e) => { setCreateFormData({ ...createFormData, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }); }; if (loading) { return (
